Direct Known Subclasses:
ModifiedBoxPlot
public abstract class RawMetric
extends Metric

An abstract base class for a metric that shows the raw verification data, rather than computing a score or showing a specific attribute of forecast quality. Examples include the modified box plot and the scatter plot.

Author:
evs@hydrosolved.com
